{"tid":2143710,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"沈大C話23800-24100會守得住","createTime":"2020-08-07T08:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T12:41:30.000Z","uid":29928,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"614718f0eddde0adb6c5630fa4b6edbd7648cb32","tid":2143710,"uid":29928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"我就放長雙眼睇定定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沈大師：看好業績惟股價不樂觀<br />\n<br />\n對於美國新打出的「科技牌」，騰訊也「中箭」，訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈認為，該股股價炒上500元以上已經「炒過龍」，認為其之前的業績無法支持其股價，加上美國國務卿蓬佩奧表明要「清網」，在兩因素配合下，相信騰訊業績前會出現較深的回吐。<br />\n<br />\n不過，沈大師指出，騰訊的衍生工具十分重倉，相信500元水平有短暫支持，但要等待騰訊即將公布的新一份業績，才能夠衡量其股價表現。他個人睇好業績會不錯，但對股價則不樂觀，「中芯份業績都靚，但股價都跌咗落嚟！」<br />\n<br />\n大市方面，沈大師仍然看好指數在大位有支持，「23800點至24000點可以守得住」。"},{"pid":"7a9eadaa953b60b20ed75fd8a1c3b5cdd71961d4","tid":2143710,"uid":258328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:12:05.000Z","msg":"留名待鞭"},{"pid":"ff84762c9ee1ab5ba862d6bd4713cb00352e8849","tid":2143710,"uid":316747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:27:58.000Z","msg":"下星期24000見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5295c582f5a957ce560637a143cc2b0dac977c5","tid":2143710,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff84762c9ee1ab5ba862d6bd4713cb00352e8849","tid":2143710,"uid":316747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:27:58.000Z","msg":"下星期24000見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:47:26.000Z","msg":"仲有成個星期五六日出招<br />\n23400啦"},{"pid":"b9d3a93dd587ee69d926329cd57ce05a8020ef98","tid":2143710,"uid":76135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:53:25.000Z","msg":"廿幾年黎的戰蹟保證"},{"pid":"c0ba470fdc02a929452b0ac2c846e3e2d2384711","tid":2143710,"uid":29928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"